-- Simmer & Jack Says Worker Killed in a Tramming Accident at Tau Lekoa Mine
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2010-10-05T12:02:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/simmer-jack-says-worker-killed-in-a-tramming-accident-at-tau-lekoa-mine.html
Simmer & Jack Mines Ltd. said a
worker was killed in a tramming accident at its Tau Lekoa mine
in South Africa on Oct. 3.  The incident will have a “minimal impact” on production,
the company said in a stock exchange statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  